Privacy Policy for [Tech Pay]

Effective Date: [23-09-2024]

1. Introduction
Welcome to [Tech Pay] We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our mobile application [Tech Pay].

2. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following types of information:

2.1. Camera Access

Purpose: The app may request access to your device's camera to enable certain functionalities such as scanning QR codes or capturing photos.
Data Usage: The images captured by your camera are processed locally on your device and are not transmitted to our servers unless explicitly shared by you.
2.2. Location Information

Purpose: The app may request access to your deviceâ€™s precise location to provide location-based services.
Data Usage: Location data is used to enhance the user experience, such as providing location-based suggestions or services. This data is processed locally and is not shared with third parties without your consent.
2.3. Internet Access

Purpose: The app may require internet access to connect to external servers for data exchange, updates, or other online features.
Data Usage: Any data transmitted over the internet is done securely, and we do not store personal data unless necessary for the functionality of the app.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:

Provide and maintain the functionality of our app.
Improve and personalize your user experience.
Communicate with you regarding updates, services, and features.
4. Sharing Your Information
We do not share your personal information with third parties except:

With your consent.
When required by law.
To protect the rights, property, or safety of our users and the public.
5. Data Security
We take reasonable steps to protect the data we collect from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

6. Your Privacy Rights
You have the right to:

Access the personal data we hold about you.
Request corrections to your personal data.
Request deletion of your personal data.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

